query:
SELECT 
  cp.id,
  cp.gestanteId,
  g.nomeCompleto,
  cp.dataConsulta,
  cp.pressaoArterialSistolica,
  cp.pressaoArterialDiastolica
FROM consultasPrenatal cp
JOIN gestantes g ON cp.gestanteId = g.id
WHERE cp.pressaoArterialSistolica >= 140 OR cp.pressaoArterialDiastolica >= 90
LIMIT 5;
